document_title: Peritoneal duct disease: Causes, diagnosis and treatment
subsection_name: benh-ly-ong-phuc-tinh-mac.json_2_Can peritoneal duct disease be prevented?
subsection_content: Peritoneal duct diseases in children are not related to nutrition, medication or lifestyle of the mother during pregnancy. Therefore, there is currently no preventative measure.

benh ly ong phuc tinh mac.json. Can peritoneal duct disease be prevented?
Peritoneal duct diseases in children are not related to nutrition, medication or lifestyle of the mother during pregnancy. Therefore, there is currently no preventative measure.
